storageJobDescription: Before creating your replication rules, ensure your replication configuration is applied retroactively to copy objects that were uploaded previously. This action triggers a job that runs in the background, and its purpose is to sync your buckets. To learn more about asynchronous replication, see the documentation
storageJobToastSuccessMessage: The synchronisation rule has been created.
storageJobToastErrorMessage: An error occurred while creating the synchronisation rule: {{message}}.
